      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and release validation consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with documented QA procedures, regression test suite passing, and traceable version control records. Meets MRL 2 SQA requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
