      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via method-of-manufactured-solutions or equivalent benchmark.",
      "rationale": "Navier-Stokes solver verified against standard CFD benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step at Reynolds numbers representative of CPB flow. Order-of-accuracy confirmed."
    },
    {
