      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be below 5% for hemolysis index QoI across three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. GCI for normalized index of hemolysis was 3.1% between medium and fine meshes. Fine mesh (12.4M cells) selected for production runs."
