      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (relative hemolysis index RH) must be directly linked to the clinical decision metric and regulatory acceptance criterion.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index RH is the direct metric for comparing device hemolysis to predicate. RH < 1 acceptance criterion maps directly to the 510(k) substantial equivalence determination. QoI is fully relevant to COU decision."
