      "rationale": "Blood analog viscosity and density measured directly with stated ±2% uncertainty. Hemolysis power-law coefficients (C, alpha, beta) sourced from Giersiepen et al. with documented uncertainty bounds. Comprehensive Monte Carlo UQ propagated all input uncertainties through the hemolysis model yielding 95% confidence interval on RH. Input characterization meets MRL 2 requirements."
