    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Comprehensive Monte Carlo UQ across all model inputs demonstrates that the predicted relative hemolysis index RH remains below 1.0 across the 95% confidence interval, supporting the worst-case hemolysis identification objective. The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
